{
  "stem": "1222.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wintertime, we used to go and try to get in, like I told you on the telephone, to the bounds where the Ukrainian people used to mix in food for the pigs.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the biggest enemies were dogs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to bark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to try to kill the dogs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mine-- mine-- Monek is one of the biggest killer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Unfortunately, he's very good nature.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But maybe he killed a lot of Arabs and things like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because to him to kill a person is like nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I would-- I'm not a killer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, he's strong, God bless him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He used to go ahead and try to choke the-- the dog.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They used to bite him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But he used to put in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyway, he used to get rid of the dogs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then when I used to go in at night time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We used to pick [INAUDIBLE], because it was around Miedzyrzecz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I knew Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We went into elderly lady.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Some of the older lady used to throw you outside a piece of bread or something just to get rid of yous.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And some of them, they used to sneak into the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "While I was talking to them, he used to push in whatever used to see, clothing and anything to thief.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We became thieves.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then later on, that's the way we survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "One day, the man came over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We came over in that [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We looked in the guy, the guy is dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we lost our third man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He-- he got sick, and he died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In hiding I was--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was hiding like that almost two and a half years, till a half a year before the liberation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- we got involved, unfortunately-- fortunately, I should say that way.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
